SELECT
	[Activity].[Id] [Id],
	[Activity].[Title] [Title],
	[Activity].[AccountId] [AccountId],
	[Account].[Name] [Account.Name],
	[Account].[AccountLogoId] [Account.AccountLogoId],
	[Activity].[StartDate] [StartDate],
	[Activity].[DueDate] [DueDate],
	[Activity].[ShowInScheduler] [ShowInScheduler],
	[Activity].[StatusId] [StatusId],
	[Status].[Name] [Status.Name],
	[Status].[Finish] [Status.Finish],
	[Activity].[ProcessElementId] [ProcessElementId],
	[Activity].[Confirmed] [Confirmed],
	[Activity].[TypeId] [TypeId],
	[Type].[Name] [Type.Name],
	(
SELECT
	COUNT([SubEntryPoint].[Id]) [Count]
FROM
	[dbo].[EntryPoint] [SubEntryPoint] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SubEntryPoint].[EntityId] = [Activity].[Id]
	AND [SubEntryPoint].[IsActive] = @P7) [SubEntryPoint]
FROM
	[dbo].[Activity] [Activity] WITH(NOLOCK)
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Account] [Account] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([Account].[Id] = [Activity].[AccountId])
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[ActivityStatus] [Status] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([Status].[Id] = [Activity].[StatusId])
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[ActivityType] [Type] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([Type].[Id] = [Activity].[TypeId])
WHERE
	((([Activity].[DueDate] >= @P1
	AND [Activity].[StartDate] <= @P2)
	AND EXISTS (
SELECT
	[ActivityParticipant].[Id] [Id]
FROM
	[dbo].[ActivityParticipant] [ActivityParticipant] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[Activity].[Id] = [ActivityParticipant].[ActivityId]
	AND (([ActivityParticipant].[InviteResponseId] <> @P3
	OR [ActivityParticipant].[InviteResponseId] IS NULL)
	AND [ActivityParticipant].[ParticipantId] = @P4)))
	AND [Activity].[ShowInScheduler] = @P5
	AND ([Activity].[TypeId] <> @P6
	OR [Activity].[TypeId] IS NULL))
ORDER BY
	[StartDate] ASC OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 300 ROWS ONLY

	[Activity].[Title] [Title],
	[Activity].[AccountId] [AccountId],
	[Account].[Name] [Account.Name],
	[Account].[AccountLogoId] [Account.AccountLogoId],
	[Activity].[StartDate] [StartDate],
	[Activity].[DueDate] [DueDate],
	[Activity].[ShowInScheduler] [ShowInScheduler],
	[Activity].[StatusId] [StatusId],
	[Status].[Name] [Status.Name],
	[Status].[Finish] [Status.Finish],
	[Activity].[ProcessElementId] [ProcessElementId],
	[Activity].[Confirmed] [Confirmed],
	[Activity].[TypeId] [TypeId],
	[Type].[Name] [Type.Name],
	(
SELECT
	COUNT([SubEntryPoint].[Id]) [Count]
FROM
	[dbo].[EntryPoint] [SubEntryPoint] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[SubEntryPoint].[EntityId] = [Activity].[Id]
	AND [SubEntryPoint].[IsActive] = @P7) [SubEntryPoint]
FROM
	[dbo].[Activity] [Activity] WITH(NOLOCK)
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Account] [Account] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([Account].[Id] = [Activity].[AccountId])
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[ActivityStatus] [Status] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([Status].[Id] = [Activity].[StatusId])
	LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[ActivityType] [Type] WITH(NOLOCK) ON ([Type].[Id] = [Activity].[TypeId])
WHERE
	((([Activity].[DueDate] >= @P1
	AND [Activity].[StartDate] <= @P2)
	AND EXISTS (
SELECT
	[ActivityParticipant].[Id] [Id]
FROM
	[dbo].[ActivityParticipant] [ActivityParticipant] WITH(NOLOCK)
WHERE
	[Activity].[Id] = [ActivityParticipant].[ActivityId]
	AND (([ActivityParticipant].[InviteResponseId] <> @P3
	OR [ActivityParticipant].[InviteResponseId] IS NULL)
	AND [ActivityParticipant].[ParticipantId] = @P4)))
	AND [Activity].[ShowInScheduler] = @P5
	AND ([Activity].[TypeId] <> @P6
	OR [Activity].[TypeId] IS NULL))
ORDER BY
	[StartDate] ASC OFFSET 0 ROWS FETCH NEXT 300 ROWS ONLY
